libcintelhex
------------------------------------------
C library for parsing Intel HEX files

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.7-1
  libcintelhex-devel-1.0+git20150723-1bl2
  libcintelhex0-1.0+git20150723-1bl2
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  CUnit-2.1.3-1
  autoconf-15-3
  automake-20250528-1
  binutils-2.46-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  libtool-2.5.4-1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/martin-helmich/libcintelhex

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/martin-helmich/libcintelhex.git

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libcintelhex-1.0+git20150723-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libcintelhex-1.0+git20150723-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libcintelhex-1.0+git20150723-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libcintelhex-1.0+git20150723-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libcintelhex0-1.0+git20150723-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libcintelhex-devel-1.0+git20150723-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libcintelhex)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libcintelhex.README
  /usr/share/doc/libcintelhex/LICENSE.txt
  /usr/share/doc/libcintelhex/README.md

(libcintelhex0)
  /usr/bin/cygcintelhex-0.dll

(libcintelhex-devel)
  /usr/include/cintelhex.h
  /usr/lib/libcintelhex.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libcintelhex.pc

